<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.5">
<l>pakalu miravun tāṉēyāyp pārum viṇṇun tāṉēyāy</l>
<l>nikaril cuṭarā yiruḷāki niṉṟār niṉṟa vūrpōlum</l>
<l>tukiliṉ koṭiyun tērttukaḷun tuṉṉi mātar kūntalvāy</l>
<l>akiliṉ pukaiyāl mukilēykku maṇiyār vīti yaḻuntūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city where stands the one who stays as day and night,</l>
<l>As the earth and the heavens, as darkness and incomparable light,</l>
<l>It seems is Aḻuntūr with beautiful streets where [fluttering] cloth banners,</l>
<l>Dust from chariots, and aquila [wood] smoke for ladies’ thick hair</l>
<l rend="indent">are the same as [on] a cloudy [day].</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
